{"tid":560220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奧巴馬辦公室收到白色粉末信件寄自香港","createTime":"2018-02-14T01:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T05:40:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0d976d0672c3e7eb7e1d297877b6e6fde64ac124","tid":560220,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T01:48:27.000Z","msg":"美國前總統奧巴馬，位於華盛頓世界自然基金會總部大樓的辦公室，亦收到藏有白色粉末的信件，當地消防部門指，白色粉末相信是嬰兒爽身粉，信件由香港寄出，並沒有寫回郵地址。事發在當地星期二中午，警方及消防接報後封鎖大樓及附近交通調查，未知奧巴馬事發時是否在辦公室內。<br />\n<br />\n今次是繼美國總統特朗普的長子收到白色粉末信件後，兩日內第二宗涉及知名政客的同類型案件。特朗普的媳婦雲妮莎，前日打開了一封含有粉末的信件，警方化驗後證實有關粉末並無危險，美國特工處正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=992964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D992964&d=nZ3leCUZjns4JbAcFq8YcG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5d08ac8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=992964</a>"},{"pid":"0f5aa52a43b5eb8e1ad074931f4aabf552dcb452","tid":560220,"uid":31841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T01:49:54.000Z","msg":"快點取消香港關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ca1d8dbd701efb2540ea395d63f19db0dc0558","tid":560220,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"嬰兒爽身粉=暗指佢孌童=pizzagate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f29044d5fc472aa71df06ecfe095bc01e67603","tid":560220,"uid":141869,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"f6ca1d8dbd701efb2540ea395d63f19db0dc0558","tid":560220,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"嬰兒爽身粉=暗指佢孌童=pizzagate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/